HEADWORD: Overalls
<hw>O"ver*alls</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
kind of loose trousers worn over others to protect them from
soiling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Waterproof leggings.</def> <rj><au>R. D.
Blackmore.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overanxiety</ent>⟦br⟧
